Do yourself a favor, enroll in ACA! The deadline for open enrollment for disaster areas ends on December 31st! If you purchase your own health insurance, this is the time when you can buy or change your health insurance plan for 2018. For most states, Americans will have until December 15th to select health insurance. For those of us affected by natural disasters this year, signing up for health insurance will almost certainly be more difficult. As a result, open enrollment in areas that have received a FEMA disaster declaration for Hurricane Harvey or other natural disasters will be able to enroll in health insurance until December 31st. #GetCovered
